caller_intent: Daniel Basso needs to obtain new home insurance after his previous policy with Main Street America canceled on October 25th.
resolution_steps: Brandi verifies Daniel's mailing address (249 Karen Circle, Winston Salem, NC 27105).
Brandi checks Daniel's insurance history, noting the cancellation date of Main Street America on October 25th.
Brandi explains the need to contact the new carrier to determine if they will accept the lapse in coverage.
Brandi estimates a 1-day timeline for underwriting review and plans to send an email to the carrier immediately.
Brandi assures Daniel that the agency will follow up once the underwriter responds, likely the next morning.
knowledge_required: Insurance underwriting processes for lapse coverage
summary: Daniel Basso seeks new home insurance after a lapse in coverage. Brandi verifies details, initiates contact with the new carrier, and schedules a follow-up once underwriting confirms acceptance of the lapse. The call concludes with Daniel satisfied and a promise to contact him tomorrow.
